@NODE "Install" "How to install the icons"
@TOC "MAIN"

 Click on @{fg shine}ClickForColors@{fg text} for the MagicWB v2.0 palette.

 Use a icon update program: MUI_IconUpdate, IconUpdate, SwazInfo or any
 other, which preserves the tooltypes and position of the icon, to update
 your old icons.
@ENDNODE

